<br>
As for rolling on loot. I rolled on the CoF when Komm raid naggy. And was close to winning to but just wanted to roll for the fun of it. I passed on it publicly. &lt;Snicker&gt; I also roll on the Rez Stick. I don’t see it as a greed item but something to better help the people I help. With the Rez stick I can rez clerics in CoG hate raids if none make it, and so on. <br>
<br>
As side for that I do it because Heamish pointed out Avenging Crusaders used to run the CoG dragon raids, we also run most of the plane raids at the time and before that my first dragon raids and plane raids where with CoG, this is my way in helping out and letting others have a chance like I did. You all don’t know how lucky you have it. On most servers Naggy and Vox are perm killed, by maybe 1 or 2 guilds. Being in a little guild like you’re in now you wouldn’t even dream about being able to go up to a plane and seeing a mini up or even a dragon.<br>
<br>
